== Install ==

See INSTALL for install first.

== Running RipL on POX with Mininet ==

RipL-POX must use the exact same topology as Mininet.  Order shouldn't matter.

# Run POX
cd ~/pox
./pox.py riplpox.riplpox --topo=ft,4 --routing=random

# Running Mininet w/a Fat Tree topology
cd ~/ripl/ripl/
sudo mn --custom mn.py --topo ft,4 --controller=remote --mac

== Verifying the setup ==

In mininet console:
pingall
iperf


